source.name: Addresses with Units - Enterprise Addressing System (EAS)
source.description:
All active addresses from the City's Enterprise Addressing System, including sub-addresses, such as units. Includes references to parcel and street centerline data.  Updated nightly.
See EAS Base Addresses for base addresses not including units.
